BUGS
- Some keyboard events aren't grabbed correctly. X timer issue
- Nadir doesn't receive any signal in key mode when a context menu is shown
  because when GTK+ creates a pop-up menu, it uses XGrabKeyboard and 
  XGrabPointer to grab the keyboard and mouse [1].

  [1] http://mail.gnome.org/archives/gtk-devel-list/2010-June/msg00154.html

NEW FEATURES
- Implement mouse mode
- Implement camera mode
- Internationalitation
- Inner scanning when using certain applications (i.e. virtual keyboard)
- (key mode) )Grab release before 2nd press
- i18n
